data.message:
Hello, Good Day, Ahoy! Eminem,  Not sure whether you personally manage this page, though I trust Gods process of bringing people together. In that, I trust your process of voiding creative suicide in those who are willing to leap above and beyond. So simply as I have grown, opening myself to to the opportunities you may provide along with the heart to see them through.🙏🏻 Much Love.❤️

[Just kept repeating the Complex, Shady Records Story Interview, particularly, the ending, with Dr Dre, Paul, just made sense, yeah 🚀]

Tell me, if I sound crazy...
